GSD.description:
btrfs: reject log replay if there is unsupported RO compat flag

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v5.15.61 by commit 89f3a8bbb4a710c257a922c6a26e49c1ccd62e85. For more details please see the references link.
